{"tid":254529,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【中銀、渣打用戶注意】銀聯ATM卡綁到Apple Pay 有咩優惠你要知","createTime":"2017-05-23T09:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T15:50:54.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3df6f7598ac1a5978004dd7dfa8bc7fe167cb86d","tid":254529,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n中銀香港（2388）及渣打（2888）公佈，其銀聯提款卡客戶，可透過Apple Pay進行支付。<br />\n<br />\n另外，兩行亦分別推出相關消費優惠。渣打公佈，由即日起至明年7月31日，渣打銀聯網絡ATM卡客戶，以Apple Pay付款，均即享1%現金回贈，最高上限為每月5,000元正，無需另外登記。<br />\n<br />\n中銀方面，由即日起至今年7月31日，首5萬名以中銀提款卡成功加入Apple Pay，並於推廣期內以該卡透過Apple Pay作最少1次消費之客戶，可獲享30元現金回贈。同時，由即日起至下月30日，到7-Eleven單一消費滿30元，並以中銀提款卡透過Apple Pay付款，即減10元。優惠不適用於購買香煙、奶粉、網上遊戲產品及服務頂目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495505649_534e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495505649_534e.jpg&h=e56518e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56729769&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56729769%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&d=ppZu%2F4t08H3ZVi%2BcUGUaq5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=746a907a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56729769%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&h=44f5a95e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56729769&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523</a>"},{"pid":"8216e63b610dba26baf0b8dc3204f293670646e6","tid":254529,"uid":2028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n中銀香港（2388）及渣打（2888）公佈，其銀聯提款卡客戶，可透過Apple Pay進行支付。<br />\n<br />\n另外，兩行亦分別推出相關消費優惠。渣打公佈，由即日起至明年7月31日，渣打銀聯網絡ATM卡客戶，以Apple Pay付款，均即享1%現金回贈，最高上限為每月5,000元正，無需另外登記。<br />\n<br />\n中銀方面，由即日起至今年7月31日，首5萬名以中銀提款卡成功加入Apple Pay，並於推廣期內以該卡透過Apple Pay作最少1次消費之客戶，可獲享30元現金回贈。同時，由即日起至下月30日，到7-Eleven單一消費滿30元，並以中銀提款卡透過Apple Pay付款，即減10元。優惠不適用於購買香煙、奶粉、網上遊戲產品及服務頂目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495505649_534e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495505649_534e.jpg&h=e56518e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56729769&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56729769%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&d=ppZu%2F4t08H3ZVi%2BcUGUaq5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=746a907a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56729769%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&h=44f5a95e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56729769&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddea8849c75f8a1c986e3efa01c24310caa849bb","tid":254529,"uid":54701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"屌試左成個鐘都加唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nscan又唔得，打card no.又點打都話我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw頭先係東亞homepage都見到atm card add左去apple pay既圖，唔知係咪用得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e194884e667def4334e877403f04f441a51c41","tid":254529,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:25:41.000Z","msg"